&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;If you worked here this past month here are some things you might have been involved in&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducting a full audit of product listings and brand content (including A+ Content) across all our Amazon storefronts to ensure consistent branding and perfect data integrity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating with our Supply Chain and Customer Happiness teams to forecast inventory needs and troubleshoot logistics queries for a major upcoming promotion.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Diving deep into Seller Central performance reports to identify trends, check account health metrics, and proactively address any potential compliance issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generating and maintaining reports on Amazon sales, operations, and competitor activity to inform the broader strategy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Updating product descriptions, images, and pricing for a new product launch across multiple international marketplaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
