&lt;li&gt;Identify and scale new local channels and partnerships to drive incremental growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Utilize BI tools and data science insights to build a rigorous view of channel effectiveness and incrementality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
