&lt;li&gt;Design and execute the roadmap for UK-specific growth initiatives and prioritise team work.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bridge the gap between the UK Brand team and Global Growth team, ensuring local needs are represented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pivot budget and strategy based on real-time performance data to drive incremental customer growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
